                {
                    "id": "rate_conversions",
                    "description": "Verifies the Section 7.4 rate-conversion diagnostics: R_ppb_hr (Eq. 7.75), R_percent_hr (Eq. 7.76), tau_SO2 (Eq. 7.78), and S_VI_production = R_total. Also checks the consistency relation: R_percent_hr / R_ppb_hr = 100 / xi_SO2 = 1e11.",
